OL,3,CActivists who block roads could be
OL,4,Cforced to pay compensation, report
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FProtesters could be forced to pay
OL,8,Fcompensation for the disruption they
OL,9,Fcause under proposals in a review by a
OL,10,FGovernment adviser.
OL,12,FIndividuals, businesses or
OL,13,Finstitutions that could show they
OL,14,Fendured loss, distress or suffering
OL,15,Ffrom an illegal protest would be
OL,16,Fentitled to court-ordered compensation
OL,17,Ffrom activists, the Daily Telegraph
OL,18,Freported.
