OL,3,CActivists who block roads could be
OL,4,Cforced to pay compensation, report
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThe measures are said to be contained
OL,8,Fin a review by Lord Walney, the
OL,9,FGovernment's adviser on political
OL,10,Fviolence and disruption, which will be
OL,11,Fpublished on Tuesday.
OL,13,FThe measures could be used to impose
OL,14,Ffinancial costs on organisations like
OL,15,FJust Stop Oil if they carry out acts
OL,16,Fsuch as blocking roads or disrupting
OL,17,Fbusinesses.
