OL,3,CActivists who block roads could be
OL,4,Cforced to pay compensation, report
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FA Home Office source told the
OL,8,FTelegraph: "If Just Stop Oil organises
OL,9,Fa major roadblock and you cannot get
OL,10,Fto work or you miss a hospital
OL,11,Fappointment, there would be a
OL,12,Fframework where you could more easily
OL,13,Fsue the organisation for the loss they
OL,14,Fhave caused you. It would be a
OL,15,Fstatutory scheme but civil action.
