OL,3,CActivists who block roads could be
OL,4,Cforced to pay compensation, report
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FA Home Office spokesman said:
OL,8,F"Extremism of any kind has no place in
OL,9,Four society and we will not tolerate
OL,10,Ftactics that set out to intimidate,
OL,11,Fthreaten or cause disruption to the
OL,12,Flaw-abiding majority.
OL,14,F"In recent months, we have also
OL,15,Fwitnessed a small number of protestors
OL,16,Fdisplay violent and hateful behaviour,
OL,17,Fand the police have our full support
OL,18,Fin tackling extremism and hate crime.
